** sch_path: /foss/designs/chipathon-2026-gf180mcu-hall-effect-sensor/xschem/ccia_top_level/b9_ccia_top_level_tb_sine.sch
**.subckt b9_ccia_top_level_tb_sine
x1 vin_p net1 net2 vin_n vout_p net3 net4 vout_n net5 phi1 phi2 net6 net7 vdd net8 vss net9 vcm ibias_main_ota_pres net10 net11
+ ibias_main_ota ibias_rrl_pres net12 net13 ibias_rrl_gm3 ibias_rrl_gm4 net14 vdd net15 net16 vdd vdd net17 net18 vdd vdd net19 net20
+ b9_ccia_top_level
C1 vout_n vss 10p
C2 vout_p vss 10p
* noconn #net1
* noconn #net2
* noconn #net3
* noconn #net4
* noconn #net5
* noconn #net6
* noconn #net7
* noconn #net8
